                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><code class="text-sm bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">cloud.region</code>, <code class="text-sm bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">cloud.account.id</code>, and <code class="text-sm bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">faas.instance</code> captured automatically — so you know exactly where an issue happened.</p>
